  "title": "Part-Time Service Crew",
  "description": "<ul><li>Provide courteous and efficient food and beverage services to the customers</li><li>Ensure cleanliness and good ambient within the restaurant and have tables ready for dine-in customers</li><li>Attend and respond to customers’ needs promptly and professionally</li><li>Answer questions or make recommendations (new products, offers) to customers</li><li>Assist in the serving of the menu-items to restaurant patrons at their seats</li><li>To work closely and cultivate strong teamwork with all colleagues and ensure smooth operations</li><li>Adhere to company’s standard operating procedures</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties and responsibilities as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Entry level candidates are welcomed</li><li>Willing to commit on weekends and public holidays</li><li>Strict sense of hygiene and safety standards</li><li>Provides good Customer Service</li><li>Basic language skills</li></ul><p>$11.50 / hr</p><p>$996 per month - 20 working hrs/week</p><p>$2192 per month - 44 working hours /week</p>",
